  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Izuno Clan <br />Your blessing is exceptionally strong, granting you abilities that others of your clan cannot replicate. <br />You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>You gain +1 to either Dex or Con.</p></li><li><p>When you move during your turn in combat, you can double your movement speed until the end of your turn.<br />After using this ability, you cannot use it again until you move 0 ft. during one of your turns.</p></li><li>Your darkvision extends to 120 ft.</li><li>You gain proficiency, or master if you alrady have proficiency, in one skill of your choice (Athletics, Acrobatics, Stealth).</li><li>You do not take damage from falling up to 50 ft., and you take half damage from falls greater than 50 ft.</li></ul>",
